[1] USA: CDC
Date: Tue 1 Sep 2020
Source: CDC, _Salmonella_ Homepage, Current Outbreaks [edited]
https://www.cdc.gov/salmonella/newport-07-20/index.html


Outbreak of _Salmonella_ Newport infections linked to onions
------------------------------------------------------------
As of 31 Aug 2020, a total of 1012 people infected with the outbreak strain of _Salmonella [enterica_ serotype] Newport have been reported from 47 states.

